<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    She's his sister. Though its heavily implied that she may also be his wife..as the Usher family never mingled with other family for generations in pro<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    She's his sister. Though its heavily implied that she may also be his wife..as the Usher family never mingled with other family for generations in producing heirs.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
